Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I select C1 to C7 vertebras on the localizer of Page 01
And	I go to Page 04 of Spine MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Transitional vertebra' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Cervical' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thoracolumbar' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lumbosacral' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Cervical' checkbox
Then 'C7 Neck rib' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Thoracolumbar' checkbox
Then 'Lumbalized TH 12' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Lumbosacral' checkbox
Then 'Lumbalized S1' radio button is enabled
And 'Sacralized L5' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Sacralized L5' radio button
Then 'Complete' radio button is enabled
And 'Incomplete' radio button is enabled
And 'Mixed' radio button is enabled
And 'Incipient' radio button is enabled
